column4: SolarCity third-quarter installations top view  costs fall
column5: Rooftop solar company SolarCity Corp   which hopes to be acquired by Tesla Motors Inc   said installations exceeded expectations in the third quarter but would come in at the low end of the company's forecast for the year.
